{
  "texts": [
    "We further computed the recall values for the relevant abstracts in the 10 generated answers and displayed them in the second row of Table 4.",
    "It is noticeable that, once again, the model that performed best is M1, with the recall of 0.64.",
    "This model cites a greater number of abstracts that contain the relevant answers compared to other models.",
    "Based solely on the recall, 0-M2 showed better results compared to M2, albeit by only 0.01.",
    "However, in one of 10 examples it did not provide any references to its elaborate answer."
  ]
}